values:
Hey!!! well it has been a while since i have updated so ill pick up where i left off. On friday i went to the football game and frankly it sucked. Most of my friends are in the band and the other friends who arnt were all fighting or with their new boyfriend. the only good part was wen the band went on break and i chilled with all my best buds (especially jess and britt). I never went to the dance cuz i was wicked tired and i hate most dances anywayz. On saturday i had practice and then we had a BBQ at the pool which sucked at first cuz there was like no food left but then billy had his father (who owns patriot pizza) bring us four pizzas. so that was awesome!! then i came home took a shower and then it was off to the American Idol concert with the fam and my aunt and two little cousins. It was ok but the best part was seeing Jasmine Trias on stage in person. she is so HOT!! she looks even better in person then on tv!! so then i come home and go online for a second and meg im's me and we talk for like 4 hours about tons of shit that needed to be discussed. i definitly think that we needed to have that convo. On sunday all i did was go to swimming a.k.a HELL for 4 hours and get the shit beat out of me. then i came home ate a shit load of food, took a nap and did homework. well thats all for now!!

c ya,

cole

hello everyone!! Lets see here from the last time i updated i have done some cool things. On saturday i went to practice and got the shit beat out of me and then i had to go to stupid ass work. work definitly sucked cuz i had to vaccum the pool and do tons of shit which SUCKED. so then these two girls that live where i work are like wanna go to the movies and i was like uh no and then they were like dom is goin so im like o ok ill go. so dom picks us up and we go see Anacondas which was good and then we brought them all home and that was saturday. On sunday i went to the Deustche Bank Golf Tournament which was awesome!!! I was almost hit by John Daly's golf ball cuz my dad was like COLE and was like wow there is a ball shit! its coming rite toward me Ahhhhhhh!!! it was funny and i was on TV!!! i also saw tiger woods and was like 2 feet away from him. and today i went to fox woods with the family. My parents gambled while me and jill walked around and hung out in a 2 floor arcade and won a shit load of tickets but the prizes sucked so we gave them to a little kid. he was like wicked happy he was acting like we just gave him a million dollars. so thats it. o and at fox woods we ate at this huge food court which had like every type of food imaginable for only 13 dollars at the door and then you could eat all you want.

c ya,

cole

Hey everyone!!!! Today was the first day of school and it was not as bad as i thot it would be! My schedule is awesome and I love all my classes. My honors physics is gonna be insanely hard tho!! but i have Hannah sittin next to me so it will be a fun time!!:) My math class is fuckin hilarious!!! it was the first day and i was almost pissing my pants. I have it double tomorrow YAY!!!! Lunch was interesting but the food was good but it was so friggin expensive i mean a slice of pizza and a water for 3 dollars thats crazy. i just attempted my physics homework lol thats a laugh and a half!! well i g2g!! c u all tomorrow at another wonderful day of school! :)lol

c ya,

Cole

hey everyone!!! i have had a very fun day today!! i will start off when i woke up and went to work. I was dreading it but my favorite person in the whole world DOM came early and we talked about arizona and all that. then i left at 3 and went to the pool to swim and i thought someone was gonna be there but no one came so i swam alone but after i swam i talked with hannah for a while which was fun. then i went back to ridgewood to meet dom and casey was there so us 3 waited for danielle to come and pick us up so she came and we went to the band show thing. we didnt stay very long but at least i got to see some of it! me, danielle, dom and casey drove around for a while and went to a cemetary and drove around some more. it was fun. then they dropped me off and here i am now. im goin to bed soon cuz i have to go back to work tomorrow morning.

cya,

cole

hey! you know what i hate?!?! THE SUN AND STUPID ANNOYING LITTLE KIDS!!! i have worked all day for 8 hours straight for 3 days now and i am burnt to a friggin crisp!! my job sucks cuz of all the stupid annoying kids that will not leave me the hell alone!!! and wen no one is at the pool i try to take a nap but i cant cuz of the drumline at band camp playing soooo friggin loud. but hey they sound better then last year so GO DRUMLINE!! actually my job isnt thaaaat bad cuz i do get free food from all the people that come swimming so that rocks. i definitly miss dom!! but she is coming home tomorrow morning so YAY!! we are goin to the band camp show thing tomorrow so that should be fun to see cuz i hear that you guyz are alot better then last year. well i am gonna go watch some olympics and eat some friggin food cuz i am starving!!

c ya,

cole

hey everyone!! today was pretty good. i was at jess's house all day working on our reports for our books and just hangin out. we had some pretty fun times lol. shes goin to band camp so i wont see her and some of my other friends for a week so that kinda sucks but watever. well thats all.

c ya,

cole

hey everyone!! today has been pretty good but it went by wicked slow. i went to the movies to see the stupid exorcist with britt, meg, and sean. it was fun but the movie was wicked dumb and britt was flipping out so me and britt left the theatre and went to papa gino's. it was nice to see britt and meg cuz i havent seen them since the last day of school. we hung out in papa gino's and talked to derek who works there and also talked to neva. then meg and sean came and we walked around then we brought britt home and here i am now. im exhausted so im gonna go read some of stupid ass drowning ruth and then go to bed!!

cya,

cole

hey! i finally have a journal cuz my profile virus is gone!! today i hung out with dom cuz she is leaving for arizona tomorrow :( :( so that sux but she will be home on wednesday. we went to friendly's and got massive ice creams that were pretty good but dom ate her whole sundae and i ate like half  lol. we saw our swim coach marc there and he payed for us!! we were very happy cuz we arnt poor now! then we went back to doms for a while and then we started walkin to ridgewood but kyle johnson picked us up so that was good! then i came home and then cruised around and went to burger king then it was off to the pool to do some swimmin with nicole! that was fun cuz i havent seen her in a while! now im home sittin here hangin out!

c ya,

cole
